    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Panoramic Vision.</strong></em> Pacithhip have large eyes that give them a 360-degree field of vision. Whenever you make a Wisdom (Perception) check related to sight, you are considered to have expertise in the Perception skill. Additionally, if you are surprised, you may act normally on your first turn. Once you’ve used this trait, you can’t use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
